{
  "stem": "10587.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And-- and because of his advice to me and all the things that he-- that he taught me, I probably am-- that's why I am alive now.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I was always cognizant of things, that something will happen, and something bad will happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because you could never expect anything good to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I have to overcome.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whatever it comes my way, I have to rise above it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because I want to see them pay for what they have done to my family, to my-- to my-- especially to my mother and father and my two brothers and-- and the rest of the family.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I always thought of-- that I am going to take revenge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There's no question about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And if this would have been the time for me to be free, that's what I probably would have done.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- but you start living again as a human.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And your thoughts are a little different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I couldn't say I was-- I was grateful that I-- that I was able to leave Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my perspective has changed somewhat, you know- that you're going to a-- to a concentration camp that is more like a forced labor camp, in my own mind.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And maybe conditions will be different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But really, they were not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By-- by cattle car.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were loaded up at Auschwitz, and we went by car to-- I think we probably arrived like the next day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were the same conditions, but not the same atmosphere, because you didn't see the pregnant women and the old people and the babies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you-- you didn't think of it the same way that, you know-- you didn't think of death.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
